# React Native Component Standards

## Directory Structure

```
screens/[Feature]Screen/
├── index.tsx              # Main screen (≤100 lines)
├── styles.ts              # StyleSheet for this screen
├── hooks/
│   ├── use[Feature]Data.ts
│   ├── use[Feature]Mutations.ts
│   └── use[Feature]Form.ts
└── components/
    ├── [Feature]Card.tsx
    ├── [Feature]Form.tsx
    ├── [Feature]List.tsx
    └── index.ts

stores/                    # Zustand stores (complex shared client state only)
└── use[Feature]Store.ts
```

## Screen Pattern

✅ **GOOD — Clean, composed screen:**

```typescript
const FeatureScreen = ({ onBack }: FeatureScreenProps) => {
  const { theme: currentTheme } = useTheme();
  const isDark = currentTheme === 'dark';
  const t = useTranslations('feature');

  const { data: items = [], isLoading } = useFeatureData();
  const { createItem } = useFeatureMutations();

  return (
    <ScreenLayout
      title={t('title')}
      gradientColors={{ light: gradients.light.feature, dark: gradients.dark.feature }}
    >
      {isLoading ? (
        <LoadingState isDark={isDark} />
      ) : items.length === 0 ? (
        <EmptyState message={t('emptyStateNoItems')} isDark={isDark} />
      ) : (
        <FeatureList items={items} isDark={isDark} />
      )}
    </ScreenLayout>
  );
};
export default FeatureScreen;
```

❌ **BAD — Monolithic screen:**

```typescript
export default function FeatureScreen() {
  // 500+ lines: inline fetch, useEffect for data, hardcoded hex colors
  const [data, setData] = useState([]);
  useEffect(() => { fetch('http://hardcoded-url/feature').then(...) }, []);
  return <View style={{ backgroundColor: '#FFFFFF' }}>...</View>;
}
```

## Component Extraction

When a component exceeds 100 lines:

1. Extract data/mutation logic → `hooks/use[Feature]Data.ts`, `use[Feature]Mutations.ts`
2. Extract form logic → `hooks/use[Feature]Form.ts`
3. Extract UI sections → sub-components in `components/`
4. Move API calls → `services/[feature].ts`

## Styles

Keep all styles in a separate `styles.ts` file. Never use inline style objects in JSX.

```typescript
// styles.ts
import { StyleSheet } from 'react-native';
export const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: { flex: 1, padding: 16 },
  card: { borderRadius: 12, padding: 16, marginBottom: 12 },
});
```

## Theme Usage

See `theme-system.mdc` — ALL colors must come from `constants/theme.ts`. Never hardcode hex values.
